snippet.title: Year of the Super Magbot Trailer
snippet.description:
Navigate your way through levels of hardcore 2D platforming… with no jump button? Super Magbot is charged with the power of magnets and ready to save the world in 2021! Wishlist the game now: https://bit.ly/3tMZTLn 

Follow on  Super Magbot Twitter: https://twitter.com/SuperMagbotGame

Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Blasphemous, The Escapists, Moving Out, Overcooked, Neon Abyss, Going Under, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. 

Visit www.team17.com for more info.
